{"title":"工欲善其事,必先利其器","uid":"7dfbca418b659e3c01ba70280331af77","slug":"config/工欲善其事","date":"2020-10-14T08:58:32.000Z","updated":"2021-12-11T02:10:04.777Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/config/工欲善其事.json","keywords":"golang rust python docker k8s","cover":[],"content":"<p>&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;俗话说的好，工欲善其事必先利其器，作为一名有追求的开发者，当然要将自己吃饭的家伙打造的即好用又美观啦。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p>&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;接下来我主要会从<code>系统软件与配置</code>,<code>Chrome插件</code>,<code>Terminal</code> 三个方面去推荐好用的软件及配置</p>\n<ul>\n<li><h4 id=\"系统软件与配置篇\"><a href=\"#系统软件与配置篇\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"系统软件与配置篇\"></a>系统软件与配置篇</h4><ul>\n<li><h5 id=\"系统软件\"><a href=\"#系统软件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"系统软件\"></a>系统软件</h5><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">name</th>\n<th align=\"center\">description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.alfredapp.com/\">Alfred4</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">提升效率的神器不过多解释了，必装</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">超级右键</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可以增强mac的右键功能，在appstore就可以下载</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Mortennn/Dozer\">Dozer</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">免费开源的隐藏图标工具</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.iterm2.com/\">iterm2</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">终端，开发人员必备</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://bjango.com/mac/istatmenus/\">iStat Menus</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">状态栏对于系统资源的监控，很好用且美观</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Foldery</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可以自定义文件夹的颜色的小工具</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Ji4n1ng/OpenInTerminal\">OpenInTerminial</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">在Finder中可以直接打开终端，编辑器</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.snipaste.com/\">Snipaste</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">截图贴图的神器，不解释</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://neatdownloadmanager.com/index.php/en/\">NeatDownloadManager</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">替代浏览器自身的下载器，可以最大开启32线程同时下载，很好用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://plumamazing.com/product/tinycal/\">Tinycal</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">一个很简洁的状态栏日历</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/jaywcjlove/awesome-mac/blob/master/README-zh.md\">Awesome-mac</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">其他mac软件</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</li>\n<li><h5 id=\"系统设置\"><a href=\"#系统设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"系统设置\"></a>系统设置</h5><ul>\n<li>通过如下命令，可以让那些包含隐藏窗口的应用程序图标变暗，从而方便我们区分<br><code>defaults write com.apple.dock showhidden -bool true; killall Dock</code></li>\n<li>恢复为默认设置<br><code>defaults delete com.apple.Dock showhidden; Killall Dock</code> </li>\n<li>开启hidpi(当外接2k 4k显示器使用时，可以调整画面更细腻舒适)<br><code>sh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xzhih/one-key-hidpi/master/hidpi-zh.sh)&quot;</code></li>\n<li>设置dock隐藏后 弹出响应时间<br><code>defaults write com.apple.Dock autohide-delay -int 0 &amp;&amp; killall Dock</code><br><code>defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-time-modifier -int 0; killall Dock</code></li>\n<li>显示与恢复隐藏文件<br><code>defaults write com.apple.finder AppleShowAllFiles -boolean true ; killall Finder</code><br><code>defaults write com.apple.finder AppleShowAllFiles -boolean false ; killall Finder</code></li>\n<li>禁止与恢复.DS_store生成<br><code>defaults write com.apple.desktopservices DSDontWriteNetworkStores -bool TRUE</code><br><code>defaults delete com.apple.desktopservices DSDontWriteNetworkStores</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><h5 id=\"other-身为开发人员必装的依赖command-line-tools\"><a href=\"#other-身为开发人员必装的依赖command-line-tools\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"other 身为开发人员必装的依赖command-line-tools\"></a>other 身为开发人员必装的依赖<code>command-line-tools</code></h5><ul>\n<li><p>命令行安装方法<br><code>xcode-select --install</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>检查是否安装成功<br><code>xcode-select --print-path</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如果命令行安装失败，可以直接去<a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/download/more/\">苹果开发者网站</a>下载安装<br><img src=\"/images/config/comline.png\" alt=\"commandline\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><h4 id=\"Chrome插件篇\"><a href=\"#Chrome插件篇\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Chrome插件篇\"></a>Chrome插件篇</h4><p>好用的插件很多，但是在经过我长时间的使用之后留下的只有下面的这些，这里也提供一个<a href=\"https://zhaoolee.gitbooks.io/chrome/content/\">谷歌插件英雄榜</a>，可以挑选适合自己的插件</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">name</th>\n<th align=\"center\">description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://adguard.com/en/welcome.html\">Adguard</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">全平台的广告拦截器，也可以只装插件，反正我是把用了许久的adblock换成这个了</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/apk-downloader-for-google/idkigghdjmipnppaeahkpcoaiphjdccm\">APK Downloader</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">用来下载google play中的软件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/file-icons-for-github-and/ficfmibkjjnpogdcfhfokmihanoldbfe\">File Icons for GitHub and GitLab</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">给github gitlab中的项目文件添加对应的图标</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://neatdownloadmanager.com/index.php/en/\">NeatDownloadMnagaer</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">NDM需要安装对应插件使用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/octotree-github-code-tree/bkhaagjahfmjljalopjnoealnfndnagc\">Octotree - GitHub code tree</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">显示github中的目录文件树，不用点来点去了，直接在侧边栏就可以看</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/simpleundoclose/emhohdghchmjepmigjojkehidlielknj\">SimpleUndoClose</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">恢复手贱关掉的网页</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%E6%B2%99%E6%8B%89%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%8D-%E8%81%9A%E5%90%88%E8%AF%8D%E5%85%B8%E5%88%92%E8%AF%8D%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91/cdonnmffkdaoajfknoeeecmchibpmkmg\">沙拉查词</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">很好用的翻译插件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/%E6%8E%98%E9%87%91/lecdifefmmfjnjjinhaennhdlmcaeeeb\">掘金</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">查看当下都有哪些流行的项目，和新项目</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo\">Tampermonkey</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">不解释 懂的都懂</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</li>\n<li><h4 id=\"Terminal\"><a href=\"#Terminal\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Terminal\"></a>Terminal</h4><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">name</th>\n<th align=\"center\">description</th>\n<th align=\"center\">install</th>\n<th align=\"center\">usage</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://brew.sh/index_zh-cn\">brew</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">不解释必装</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash -c “$(curl -fsSL <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)&quot;\">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)&quot;</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew –help</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh\">ohmyzsh</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">不解释必装</td>\n<td align=\"center\">sh -c “$(curl -fsSL <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)&quot;\">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)&quot;</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#x2F;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr\">tldr</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">有啥命令不会用了就直接用它查看，还有使用示例</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install tldr</td>\n<td align=\"center\">tldr wget</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/dbcli/mycli\">mycli</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">mysql增强客户端可以自动补全，记录历史，彩色</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install mycli</td>\n<td align=\"center\">同mysql-client</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/busyloop/lolcat\">lolcat</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">炫彩的cat</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install lolcat</td>\n<td align=\"center\">…</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/httpie/httpie\">httpie</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">功能同curl,但是要好用许多</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install httpie</td>\n<td align=\"center\">http –help</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href>cmatrix</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">装逼</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install cmatrix</td>\n<td align=\"center\">cmatrix</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sharkdp/fd\">fd</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">增强的find，比find要快很多</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install fd</td>\n<td align=\"center\">fd –help</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/dalance/procs\">procs</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">比ps更好用</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install procs</td>\n<td align=\"center\">procs docker</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href>htop</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">众所周知的东西了</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install htop</td>\n<td align=\"center\">htop</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/dylanaraps/neofetch\">neofetch</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">终端输出美化的电脑配置图</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install neofetch</td>\n<td align=\"center\">neofetch</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">telnet，tree</td>\n<td align=\"center\">mac 自带没有这些工具</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#x2F;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/ggreer/the_silver_searcher\">the_silver_searcher</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">用来搜索文件中字符串的工具</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install</td>\n<td align=\"center\">ag –help</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href>ncdu</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">交互式查看文件的工具</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install</td>\n<td align=\"center\">ncdu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/cgag/loc\">loc</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">统计代码行数</td>\n<td align=\"center\">brew install</td>\n<td align=\"center\">loc .</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/afc163/fanyi\">fanyi</a></td>\n<td align=\"center\">命令翻译工具</td>\n<td align=\"center\">npm install fanyi -g</td>\n<td align=\"center\">fanyi xxx</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;俗话说的好，工欲善其事必先利其器，作为一名有追求的开发者，当然要将自己吃饭的家伙打造的即好用又美观啦。 &amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;接下来我主要会从...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"工具配置","slug":"工具配置","count":1,"path":"api/categories/工具配置.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"mac","slug":"mac","count":1,"path":"api/tags/mac.json"},{"name":"config","slug":"config","count":1,"path":"api/tags/config.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%AF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">系统软件与配置篇</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">系统软件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">系统设置</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#other-%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E5%BF%85%E8%A3%85%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96command-line-tools\"><span class=\"toc-text\">other 身为开发人员必装的依赖command-line-tools</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Chrome%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E7%AF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Chrome插件篇</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Terminal\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Terminal</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img